SUMMARY:Rhythm Fitness
LOCATION:Forest Hills Recreation Center 724 W 109th Ave. Tampa \, FL 33612
  United States
DESCRIPTION:Rhythm Fitness is a great event of fitness\, fun\, and friends
 . Registration begins at 8 am\, with a walk at 8:30. High-impact aerobics 
 begin at 9:15. Coach Arthur will make sure its a great time - what better 
 way to get healthier? Join us for Rhythm Fitness  a highenergy Saturday mo
 rning workout led by our very own Arthur Hopson from Parks Recreation! Thi
 s spring series is all about fun\, fitness\, and community. Why Youll Love
  It:  Fun\, upbeat\, musicdriven workouts  Perfect for beginners and seaso
 ned movers  A welcoming community atmosphere  Help us share! Lets get the 
 word out and encourage residents to join us for these upbeat weekend worko
 uts. Bonus: With a City of Tampa Rec Card starting at just 15 a year \, yo
 u can access fitness rooms\, open gym\, and more all year long. Lets make 
 this the year we prioritize health\, happiness\, and movement together. Se
 e you on the dance floor\, Tampa! \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/nod
 e/186921
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/186921
END:VEVENT
